@page "/"

<div class="landing">

    <h1>
        Emotion Analyzer AI
    </h1>

    <p class="subtitle">
        AI-powered text emotion recognition system
    </p>


    <div class="card">

        <h2>
            About the project
        </h2>

        <p>
            Emotion Analyzer is an application that uses
            machine learning to recognize emotions from text.
            The system analyzes the provided sentence and
            predicts the probability of different emotions.
        </p>

        <p>
            The project was created using:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>ASP.NET Core Web API</li>
            <li>Blazor Web App</li>
            <li>ML.NET Machine Learning</li>
            <li>Docker + Render deployment</li>
        </ul>

    </div>



    <div class="card">

        <h2>
            How does the model work?
        </h2>


        <p>
            The user enters a text message.
            The application sends it to the API,
            where the machine learning model analyzes
            the text.
        </p>


        <ol>
            <li>Text preprocessing</li>
            <li>Machine learning prediction</li>
            <li>Emotion probability calculation</li>
            <li>Displaying the final result</li>
        </ol>


    </div>



    <div class="card">

        <h2>
            Supported emotions
        </h2>

        <div class="emotions">

            <span>😄 Joy</span>
            <span>😢 Sadness</span>
            <span>😡 Anger</span>
            <span>😨 Fear</span>
            <span>❤️ Love</span>
            <span>😮 Surprise</span>

        </div>

    </div>


</div>